### Typography (from Plectrum Fonts doc)
- **Base font size**: `1rem = 14px`
- **Display / Heading font**: `Agenda` (`--font-agenda`)
- **Body / Label font**: `Open Sans` (`--font-open-sans`)
- Font styles follow the pattern: `text-{category}-{size}` (e.g. `text-body-sm`, `text-heading-lg`)
- Always use Plectrum text style tokens — never hardcode `font-size` or `font-family`

### Design Tokens (from Plectrum tokens doc)
- Tokens are automatically provided by implementing the Plectrum PrimeNG theme via `providePlectrum()`
- Always reference semantic tokens (e.g. `{primary.color}`) — never hardcode hex values
- Never reference primitive tokens (e.g. `{gray.600}`) when a component token exists
- When in doubt about a token, inspect the Figma UI Kit via Figma MCP

